 0.70710678118655
%filt_H0 - symmetric
 0, 0.70710678118655
 1, 0.70710678118655
%filt_H1 - antisymmetric
 0,-0.70710678118655
 1, 0.70710678118655
%filt_G0 - can be deduced from filt_H1
%filt_G1 - can be deduced from filt_H0

